    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "CXR\nLaterally displaced scapula\nAssociated with distracted\nclavicle fracture\n, AC spearation, sternoclavicular dislocation\nCT Chest\nTo identify intrathoracic injuries\nCT Angio\nTo detect vascular injuries",
      "subsections": {},
